  "text": "We performed initial experiments for sketch-based search on the FERET face database [CITATION_1] , containing 12,000 pictures taken from 1,200 human faces. As illustrated in Fig. 13 , our SBIR system provides acceptable to good results even when applied in such a specialized search scenario. Controlling the visual search processes through sketch lines opens the question of the drawing interface provided to usersadditional computation (i.e., symmetry enforcement, filtering) could help to improve retrieval results in this scenario.",
